Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.47,0:01:16.01,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}物語は終わり
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.01,0:01:18.35,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}勇者は眠りにつく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.35,0:01:21.06,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}穏やかな日常を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.06,0:01:22.90,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}この地に残して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.90,0:01:25.11,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}時の流れは無情に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.11,0:01:27.48,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}人を忘れさせる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.48,0:01:30.20,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}そこに生きた軌跡も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.20,0:01:31.99,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}錆び付いていく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.99,0:01:33.99,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}それでも君の
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.99,0:01:36.20,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}言葉も願いも勇気も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.20,0:01:39.50,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}今も確かに私の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.50,0:01:41.66,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}生きている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.25,0:01:43.88,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}同じ途を選んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.88,0:01:45.96,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}それだけだったはずなのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.96,0:01:47.59,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}いつの間にかどうして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.59,0:01:52.09,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}頬を伝う涙の理由をもっと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.09,0:01:53.30,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}知りたいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.30,0:01:54.26,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}今更だって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.26,0:01:56.76,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}共に歩んだ旅路を辿れば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.76,0:02:00.18,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}そこに君は居なくとも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.18,0:02:02.27,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}きっと見つけられる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:47.19,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}就像童話故事裡那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.19,0:00:49.49,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}一切迎來結束的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.49,0:00:52.37,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}從漫長旅途中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.37,0:00:53.95,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}截取出來的一小節
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.95,0:00:56.41,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}很久以前邪惡的陰影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.41,0:00:58.50,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}籠罩了這片土地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.50,0:01:01.08,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}這是與討伐邪惡的勇者的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.08,0:01:03.50,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}短暫旅途的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.47,0:01:16.01,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}故事結束
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.01,0:01:18.35,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}勇者沉眠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.35,0:01:21.06,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}平穩的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.06,0:01:22.90,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}留給這片土地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.90,0:01:25.11,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}時光流逝如梭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.11,0:01:27.48,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}帶走人的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.48,0:01:30.20,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}你刻下的道道軌跡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.20,0:01:31.99,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}也漸漸染上鏽斑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.99,0:01:33.99,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}儘管如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.99,0:01:36.20,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}你說過的話 你的願望和勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.20,0:01:39.50,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}現在也毫無疑問
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.50,0:01:41.66,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}在我心中迴盪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.25,0:01:43.88,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}踏上同一條旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.88,0:01:45.96,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}明明沒什麼特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.96,0:01:47.59,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}卻讓我眼角含淚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.59,0:01:52.09,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}不知何時起 我變得想要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.09,0:01:53.30,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}這一切的緣由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.30,0:01:54.26,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}哪怕已經太遲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.26,0:01:56.76,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}只要再次踏上與你走過的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.76,0:02:00.18,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}哪怕你已經不在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.18,0:02:02.27,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}也一定能夠找到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.09,0:22:51.97,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}And you alright
